{"tid":281922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"32D人妻Kimi性感闖娛圈　獲老公開綠燈","createTime":"2017-06-13T04:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T02:02:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6584a29e6c233dcbc361f2e2e3b65ada07950af9","tid":281922,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276119_7b37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276119_7b37.jpg&h=34b83e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n採訪：卓寶花 攝影：陳慧安 錄影：廖達燊<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276120_8515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276120_8515.jpg&h=6baf570a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi做過平面模特兒，曾做o靚模出寫真，其後接受整容。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276122_f7a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276122_f7a3.jpg&h=91f38caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi曾參選ViuTV《美選D.n.A》，有翻版謝安琪之稱。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276124_d799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276124_d799.jpg&h=31301515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi話唔怕行性感<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276125_c17b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276125_c17b.jpg&h=080d9d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最緊要意識健康<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276127_b3c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276127_b3c6.jpg&h=53f8caa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi舊年同圈外男友結婚<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276129_0fc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276129_0fc6.jpg&h=d6f1efff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi話喺鏡頭前嗌交叻，但人後佢可以好小鳥依人。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276130_0364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276130_0364.jpg&h=e9b64a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276132_cc78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276132_cc78.jpg&h=9176c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKimi嘅人妻身份無礙喺娛圈發展<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497276133_0fb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497276133_0fb6.jpg&h=66da7cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年25歲D Cup人妻趙詠瑤（Kimi）參加ViuTV《美選D.n.A》後繼續留喺ViuTV做節目主持，人妻身份無礙發展，反而得到力捧，由o靚模躍升到做主持拍電影。Kimi曾大膽承認整容，現擁32D豐滿上圍配以嬌滴玲瓏身材，面對鏡頭即密集擺甫，十分嬌嗲，人妻魅力依然吸引。<br />\n<br />\nKimi主持ViuTV節目《晚吹&mdash;男人講嘢》同《Out畢豬仔團》，喺《晚吹》節目中，會和灘叔（鄒凱光）鬥嘴，要口才腦筋靈活，Kimi說：「我鬧交叻梗係叻，唔係點樣食住我身邊男人，大家人前人後，喺人前佢會就我，適當時我亦會小鳥依人。」Kimi認為婚後工作反而更順利，因為可以俾到更多安全感俾另一半，令對方安心，即使要同異性有親密演出都冇問題。<br />\n<br />\nKimi唔介意在圈中性感演出，並說：「聽聞電影《同囚》想添食，如果要我拍女版游學修露股、露背我都OK，主要體意識，劇情需要又唔鹹濕就得啦！老公都係睇意識，如果亂俾人摸係唔值得，佢會好介意，但意識健康佢就話之你被強姦。」<br />\n稍後大家會睇到Kimi在冰川着上泳衣喺節目中出鏡，最初以為節目歐遊可以好暢快，後來為滿足拍檔要喺當地打工接受考驗。<br />\n<br />\n姓名：趙詠瑤（Kimi）<br />\n年齡：25歲<br />\n三圍：32D、25、36<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170613/56819730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170613%2F56819730&d=uHgUlRXO4nbkmtt%2BWAbK4YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=49371b2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170613%2F56819730&h=d3b9c186\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170613/56819730</a>"},{"pid":"576909df13e5d0855aafdf9a12274781e7d17a58","tid":281922,"uid":70505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"塊pad 厚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61dcdc985b93eeb7c0f4172d49d89f0d263237f","tid":281922,"uid":33809,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"整容，隆胸，生仔，全部做齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaff1dcdb833b46ee1ea95158210fc275ae90801","tid":281922,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整容，隆胸，生仔，全部做齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法官大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f78680dcd4b470fc6827974ad98826285e23dd5","tid":281922,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"親大台傳媒，吹捧大台旗下性感女演員；<br />\n所以生果傳媒，就捧另外兩間免費台嘅女藝員