ime":"2017-06-13T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"佢影相個表情好撚作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795cd7b612ea2a02e82dce6fdb361c2289be7e31","tid":281922,"uid":89131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"佢同骨精強啲片幾好睇"},{"pid":"66fa55f8e0f6bd97cb97a7e074feaf90601609e8","tid":281922,"uid":29283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都D係咪戇鳩, c都畀多啦</blockquote><br />\n撚有d 再講唔高既女大波好柒"},{"pid":"0a8e0cbdccd481d354da26e9571ba085f4ad6dc1","tid":281922,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:44:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>《收嗲啦！八婆》網絡爆紅　人妻Kimi認整過容</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267895_9341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267895_9341.jpg&h=6449767b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267896_bcf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267896_bcf9.jpg&h=b449b4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267899_fc70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267899_fc70.jpg&h=59865c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參加《美選D.n.A.》十二強不入(資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267900_9ba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267900_9ba2.jpg&h=8e570f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267902_c4b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267902_c4b9.jpg&h=a4f7e91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《收嗲啦！八婆》可能引起咗唔少男友嘅心聲<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267904_16df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267904_16df.jpg&h=df291afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267905_f862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267905_f862.jpg&h=c03bafa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我今日有咩唔同啊？」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267906_7fe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267906_7fe3.jpg&h=e4690a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497267907_0c62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497267907_0c62.jpg&h=71987030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙詠瑤Kimi Chiu呢個名，大家喺邊度認識佢呢？可能有部份會係佢參加過ViuTV嘅《美選D.n.A.》，但如果講到最近的話，一定會係喺社交網絡瘋傳嘅《收嗲啦！八婆》系列喇。<br />\n<br />\nKimi雖然喺《美選D.n.A.》入面，十二強嘅時候已經被淘汰，但都有引起過大眾嘅關注，因為佢大方承認整過容，而喺複試3日後（27日）已榮升做人妻，當時喺ViuTV嘅介紹入面，仲叫做「重塑型D cup已婚人妻」。<br />\n<br />\n不過喺4月嘅時候，佢就喺facebook同youtube好活躍，佢同埋專門講AV嘅網絡人「骨精強」，合作拍咗《收嗲啦！八婆》系列，喺片入面，Kimi就演一個港女到不得了嘅女朋友，對男朋友無理取鬧，演男朋友嘅「骨精強」就大鬧佢：「收嗲啦！八婆。」可能係因為同香港情侶好有共鳴，所以短短兩個月，呢個系列嘅片已經去到百幾萬點擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170613/56819312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170613%2F56819312&d=uHgUlRXO4nbkmtt%2BWAbK4YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c1fcb424\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170613%2F56819312&h=98e1187b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170613/56819312</a>"},{"pid":"b6c7b607e33f67c928b4fd0f15d47878b3bd83a7","tid":281922,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:50:31.000Z","msg":"正淫閪， 拍av 啦 夫目前犯"},{"pid":"ad9eb4caa2c56e7fe6ea08cb5e8bbae45eb3859b","tid":281922,"uid":6675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"阿婆屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2161d43ea25496cbd4863c4c7c9918f3122ca3d3","tid":281922,"uid":76040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"屌 條女以前我同學<br />\n未整容之前好撚樣衰 唔化妝嚇撚死人<br />\n又發明星夢唔翻學唔做project 做free rider<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c331f82d1590a640779649b6a6dd05542cf8c89","tid":281922,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T19:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊撚度有D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係"},{"pid":"80131107770020dd8570895c5ba4fbad31d823bb","tid":281922,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:00:38.000Z","msg":"我屌"},{"pid":"fcb20b69a3e04f7646e4049e54f1970a44a9e95f","tid":281922,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T22:29:31.000Z","msg":"你唔做雞我點養你呀"},{"pid":"2c02d5c4f1f97508fb587a6e61e08ec1ef52f322","tid":281922,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T22:32:24.000Z","msg":"不了"}]}